{
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content-editor-core lake-engine lake-typography-classic\" data-lake-element=\"root\"><p data-lake-id=\"a20d224c568e48b9d67847a2c66a8c01_p_0\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">PDO::lastInsertId — 返回最后插入行的ID或序列值</p><p data-lake-id=\"587d2b231fcd2c21a9550fe22eb273cb\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"d5019569e5a5b92f9806b5482dafad0b\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">PDO::lastInsertId 方法返回是有条件的，默认情况下他是返回 <span style=\"color: #F5222D;\">主键且自增长的字段值</span>，否则返回0，而文档中并未说明。</p><p data-lake-id=\"dcdba017553189f0f858b5291eb24e1d\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"c902fd804cdeb73fdb69faaf34798f31\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">php中PDO::lastInsertId的实现 是调用mysql api中的 mysql_insert_id 函数，而该函数有详细说明。</p><p data-lake-id=\"b477b8ca36e179afd5378c697e8b2e38\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"616dd2b0242e1897ffebb05b9944e782\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">下面是php中对mysql_insert_id 函数说明：</p><p data-lake-id=\"6461dd9a79805327d71b8956a4885f12\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p class=\"\" data-lake-id=\"e821732c5a1578a2a7c740094c58744a\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span data-card-type=\"inline\" data-lake-card=\"image\" class=\"lake-card-margin-top lake-card-margin-bottom\"><img data-role=\"image\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/491128/1588060838295-7a721422-b713-41cc-b46d-e4b02c0645b9.png\" data-raw-src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/491128/1588060838295-7a721422-b713-41cc-b46d-e4b02c0645b9.png\" class=\"image lake-drag-image\" alt=\"2129764801.png\" title=\"2129764801.png\" style=\"visibility: visible; border: none; box-shadow: none; width: 746px; height: 151px;\"></span></p><p data-lake-id=\"14f6f9d556945cda2f55d87ddaa38851\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p></div>",
